# Flat AST Bridge
#
# Converts the core parser's flat, index-based AST into the richer frontend
# Module shape expected by HIR lowering. This is used as the bootstrap-safe
# frontend path when the newer parser surface is unavailable.

# Split from src/compiler/10.frontend/flat_ast_bridge.spl to keep module cohesion under the 800-line source limit.
export use compiler.frontend.flat_ast_bridge_part1.*
export use compiler.frontend.flat_ast_bridge_part2.*
